# React (Vite SPA)

- Define components with `function ComponentName()`, not arrow components.
- Extract reusable logic into `src/hooks/use-*.js`; keep `App.jsx` as composition, not a monolith.
- Colocate styles in CSS modules or existing `App.css` classes; avoid inline styles except canvas/DOM necessities.
- `useEffect`: always return cleanup for subscriptions, timers, and `addEventListener`.
- `useCallback` / `useMemo` only when profiling or stabilizing deps for memoized children — not by default.
- List keys: stable ids, never array index for mutable lists.
- File input handlers: `handleFileChange`, not anonymous mega-handlers in JSX when logic is non-trivial.

```jsx
// Prefer
function Sidebar({ onFileSelect }) {
  function handleFileChange(event) {
    const file = event.target.files?.[0]
    if (!file) return
    onFileSelect(file)
  }
  return <input type="file" onChange={handleFileChange} />
}
```

Pure ArchiMate/XML/diagram math belongs in `src/lib/archimate/`, not in components.
